---

<section class="cta-banner" id="cta">
  <div
    class="cta-banner-card"
    style="background-image: url('/plombier.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat; min-height: 360px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"
  >
    <div class="cta-banner-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="cta-banner-inner">
      <span class="cta-banner-badge">DÉPANNAGE EN MOINS DE 30 MIN</span>
      <h2 class="cta-banner-title">Besoin d'un plombier maintenant ?</h2>
      <p class="cta-banner-subtitle">Appelez le 01 89 70 96 34 pour une intervention immédiate.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-banner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 60px 16px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cta-banner-card {
    position: relative;
    max-width: calc(100% - 24px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    box-shadow:
      0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3),
      0 0 40px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .cta-banner-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-banner-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .cta-banner-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.3);
    color: #93c5fd;
    border: 1px solid rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.4);
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta-banner-title {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(24px, 6vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .cta-banner-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Chelsea Market', cursive;
    font-size: clamp(13px, 3.5vw, 15px);
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta-banner {
      padding: 40px 12px;
    }

    .cta-banner-card {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 16px;
      min-height: 280px;
    }

    .cta-banner-inner {
      padding: 48px 16px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta-banner-card {
      animation: none !important;
    }
  }
</style>
